    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''Eighty-five is nothing. Eighty-five is young. Eighty-five is 15 years away from 100.''</p>
        <p>THOMAS PERLS, geriatrician leading a Harvard University study of centenarians.</p>
        <p>[A1]</p>
